MessageJP: アスナ
MessageEN: Asuna

MessageJP: 既読
MessageEN: Message read

MessageJP: 大変！
MessageEN: We have a problem, Master! A big problem!

MessageJP: 大変だよご主人様！今すぐ助けて！
MessageEN: I need your help! It's an emergency!
Is the emergency that you're bored?

MessageJP: ど、どうしたの……？
MessageEN: I guess peace is its own problem...

MessageJP: え？
MessageEN: Oh.

MessageJP: 今の私、どうしたんだろ？
MessageEN: What are you talking about? What am I talking about?
...What?

MessageJP: ど、どういうこと……？
MessageEN: Did you forget our conversation while we were still having it?

MessageJP: あ
MessageEN: Well...

MessageJP: うん
MessageEN: Yeah.

MessageJP: そう！そんな感じ！
MessageEN: Yeah! Looks like that's exactly what happened!

MessageJP: 今回は本当だよ、本当に助けが
MessageEN: For real this time, like really real, I really need help!

MessageJP: 必要
MessageEN: Needed.

MessageJP: あれ？どうしたの、ご主人様？
MessageEN: Huh? What's going on?

MessageJP: 何かあった？
MessageEN: Master?

MessageJP: アスナの絆イベントへ
MessageTW: 前往明日奈的羈絆劇情
MessageEN: Go to Asuna's Event

MessageJP: とうちゃーく！
MessageEN: I'm home!

MessageJP: ご主人様はちゃんとシャーレまで戻れた？
MessageTW: 主人平安回到夏萊了嗎？
MessageEN: Did you get back okay? Everything went so well thanks to you!

MessageJP: 今日はおかげで助かったけど、なんて言うか、ごめんね
MessageTW: 今天雖然託你的福得救了，不過該怎麼說呢，真抱歉
MessageEN: I feel guilty always relying on you.

MessageJP: 気にしないで、私はアスナの先生だから
MessageTW: 不用放在心上，我是明日奈的老師呀
MessageEN: Don't worry about it. Being relied on is part of the job.

MessageJP: まあ、その、怒ってないなら良かった……
MessageEN: As long as you're comfortable with it.

MessageJP: でも、どうして急に治ったんだろうね？
MessageTW: 不過，為什麼突然就治好了呢？
MessageEN: But why bring it up? Something on your mind?

MessageJP: うーん、そういえばあの時……
MessageTW: 唔嗯，這麼說來那個時候……
MessageEN: Hmm... I'm not entirely sure myself...

MessageJP: まあ、とりあえずご主人様のおかげで助かったことは確かだね！
MessageTW: 總之，多虧有主人才得救這件事是真的呢！
MessageEN: The important thing is that you helped!

MessageJP: メイドさんとして、そのお礼のご奉仕をたくさんしないと！
MessageTW: 身為女僕，得用很多侍奉來報答才行！
MessageEN: And a maid's job is to serve, so there'll be plenty of chances to repay the favor! I'll make sure of it!

MessageJP: じゃあまたね、ご主人様！
MessageEN: See you later, Master!

MessageJP: あらためて、今日は本当にありがとう！
MessageTW: 再說一次，今天真的非常感謝！
MessageEN: Again, thank you so much!
